    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spaceborne Fighters is a dynamic arena platformer that combines fast-paced action with strategic choices. Fight on unique maps, develop your characters, experiment with random skills, and craft powerful items to dominate every arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/27fedb81450e49cdecbdd264f2d2bdc5.poster.avif?t=1764593286\" width=608 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/27fedb81450e49cdecbdd264f2d2bdc5.webm?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/27fedb81450e49cdecbdd264f2d2bdc5.mp4?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 maps with unique layouts and challenges,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 heroes with individual skill trees,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >random skills gained during gameplay,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >item crafting that affects your gameplay,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >dynamic, fast-paced action on the arenas,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >the ability to develop characters and create different builds.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enter the Arena</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/de4f85e32fae52eafb774ab8d4b72eca.poster.avif?t=1764593286\" width=608 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/de4f85e32fae52eafb774ab8d4b72eca.webm?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/de4f85e32fae52eafb774ab8d4b72eca.mp4?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through 10 diverse maps — each with its own style, obstacles, and enemy types. Every battle brings new pacing, new threats, and new decisions that can determine your victory or defeat.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/fb7b011f01755fcd702ce4b27345f455.poster.avif?t=1764593286\" width=608 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/fb7b011f01755fcd702ce4b27345f455.webm?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/fb7b011f01755fcd702ce4b27345f455.mp4?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gradually uncover the stories of each of the 10 heroes — their past, their relationships, and the reasons that brought them to the arenas. The narrative unfolds through short scenes, dialogues, and unlockable entries, allowing you to better understand the characters’ motivations and the world of Spaceborne Fighters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character Progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/e90984a6106084fd2d41971dafb9d7da.poster.avif?t=1764593286\" width=608 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/e90984a6106084fd2d41971dafb9d7da.webm?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/e90984a6106084fd2d41971dafb9d7da.mp4?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of the 10 playable heroes — each with their own skill tree that you upgrade permanently. Earn points, unlock new abilities, and build your character to match your preferred playstyle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Random Skills During Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/3b049b34f4a06d2b618a79123e28e102.poster.avif?t=1764593286\" width=608 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/3b049b34f4a06d2b618a79123e28e102.webm?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/3b049b34f4a06d2b618a79123e28e102.mp4?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During battles, you gain levels and draw temporary skills that change the course of the round. Each playthrough is different — every combination brings new possibilities and new strategies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Crafting and Items</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/5f63f2a23bbbaed16634b22c9c80c513.poster.avif?t=1764593286\" width=608 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/5f63f2a23bbbaed16634b22c9c80c513.webm?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104780/extras/5f63f2a23bbbaed16634b22c9c80c513.mp4?t=1764593286\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources after each battle and craft powerful items that significantly affect gameplay. Experiment with combinations and find item sets that help you take on even the toughest hordes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>10 Diverse Heroes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character offers:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >unique abilities,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a distinct combat style,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >their own skill tree,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >different pacing and gameplay dynamics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the hero that perfectly fits your playstyle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become the Greatest Warrior in the Cosmos</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spaceborne Fighters offers a blend of fast-paced action, dynamic decision-making, and deep progression. Enter the arena, develop your skills, and overcome everything that stands in your way.</p>",
